divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving south on US 101 and looked over towards the SFO airport area and a shiny reflective object caught my eye. After several takes, it was a donut shaped metallic object that was tilting left and then right while rotating. As I was moving I couldn't tell if it was moving too but it seemed to be hovering. It was high up in the sky but not too high as I was able to see it's shape (donut) and movement very clearly. I couldn't watch it for long as I was on a highway but it was definitely there. Possibly it was a kite or something man made but since it was right next to SFO I'm assuming that wouldn't be allowed due to clearance issues. I contacted SFO airport with inquiries but I didn't receive any response.
Summary: Donut shaped metallic ufo over SFO Airport
